<template><div><h1 id="installation-guide-to-tohe-on-xbox-app" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#installation-guide-to-tohe-on-xbox-app"><span><font color=#f0b6d5>Installation Guide to TOHE on: <font color=#0e7a0d>Xbox App</font></font></span></a></h1>
<p>It appears you want to install TOHE on Xbox App! Lucky for you, you're in the right place.<br>
Follow these simple steps, and TOHE will be working in no-time at all!</p>
<p>NOTE: This is for the <code v-pre>Xbox App</code> version of Among Us. You cannot download TOHE on the Microsoft Store version of Among Us. TOHE cannot be downloaded on Xbox Consoles.</p>
<h3 id="step-1-download-the-latest-release" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#step-1-download-the-latest-release"><span><font color=#f0b6d5><font color=#0e7a0d>Step 1:</font> Download the Latest Release</font></span></a></h3>
<p>Download the latest full Release of Town of Host: Enhanced in our Discord at <code v-pre>#tohe-release</code>, or on our GitHub <a href="https://github.com/0xDrMoe/TownofHost-Enhanced/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Here<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>. (Make sure you install the <code v-pre>TOH-Enhanced-XboxApp-2.2.0.zip</code> &amp; not <code v-pre>TOH-Enhanced-SteamEpic-2.2.0.zip</code>.)</p>
<h3 id="step-2-extract-the-mod-folder" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#step-2-extract-the-mod-folder"><span><font color=#f0b6d5><font color=#0e7a0d>Step 2:</font> Extract the Mod Folder</font></span></a></h3>
<p>Once the download is complete, extract it into a new empty folder somewhere, like on the desktop.</p>
<h3 id="step-3-copy-paste-your-mod-files-into-game-directory" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#step-3-copy-paste-your-mod-files-into-game-directory"><span><font color=#f0b6d5><font color=#0e7a0d>Step 3:</font> Copy + Paste your Mod Files into Game Directory</font></span></a></h3>
<p>Locate your AmongUs install. Firstly you need to go to Xbox App, then you can find this by right clicking on the game in your Library, selecting <i>Manage</i>, then <i>Files</i>, and finally selecting <i>Browse files</i>.<br>
<img src="@source/images/MSGetFolder.png" alt="image"></p>
<p>Select all of the files in your TOHE folder and copy them to the Among Us installation folder. The folder should now look something like this:<br>
<img src="@source/images/MSResultFolder.png" alt="image"></p>
<h3 id="step-4-run-among-us-to-set-up-the-mod" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#step-4-run-among-us-to-set-up-the-mod"><span><font color=#f0b6d5><font color=#0e7a0d>Step 4:</font> Run Among Us to Set Up the Mod</font></span></a></h3>
<p>Now go back to Xbox App, then launch the game like you would normally do. Theres no problem in launching the game with <i>Among Us.exe</i> at all.<br>
Note: You shouldn't run into the 'you are logged out/in offline mode' issue as TOHE <i>has</i> to be in your Xbox App folder and cannot be separated. You can play Vanilla as usual by clicking the Settings Wheel in the top-right of the window, and swapping to Vanilla.</p>
<h3 id="step-5-create-a-shortcut-optional" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#step-5-create-a-shortcut-optional"><span><font color=#f0b6d5><font color=#0e7a0d>Step 5:</font> Create a Shortcut <font color=#ed3d52>[OPTIONAL]</font></font></span></a></h3>
<p>Right click your <i>Among Us.exe</i> file and click <i>Create shortcut</i>. Then, move the new shortcut to a location thatâ€™s easy for you to access, such as your Desktop.</p>
